<\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip:<\/strong> Go out into the rural villages and meet the people that give Kerala its name. Eat with a family in a homestay, help out in the village, and learn about this extraordinary corner of India.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/46553&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105809\/kerala-india-top-reasons-to-visit.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105809\/kerala-india-top-reasons-to-visit-19x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105809\/kerala-india-top-reasons-to-visit-376x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"Best Reasons to Visit Kerela, India\" height=\"600\" width=\"376\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-to-explore-the-backwaters-by-boat\">To Explore the Backwaters by Boat<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Kerala is characterized by its famous backwaters: calm lagoons and rivers that interlace in a stunning waterways network. Start in Alleppey, or Kumarakom, and spend a few days staying on a traditional houseboat. Enjoy sailing the calm river, spotting exotic wildlife among the palm tree forests, and colorful birds skim the waters. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105846\/karela-india-boat-tour.jpg\" alt=\"kerala india boat tour\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"kerala india boat tour\" class=\"wp-image-46694 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105846\/karela-india-boat-tour.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105846\/karela-india-boat-tour-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105846\/karela-india-boat-tour-600x401.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105846\/karela-india-boat-tour-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105846\/karela-india-boat-tour-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105846\/karela-india-boat-tour-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105846\/karela-india-boat-tour-1536x1026.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105846\/karela-india-boat-tour-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105846\/karela-india-boat-tour-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/upload