mbed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe title=\"Human by Nature | Kerala Tourism\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/dt2q75pauBo?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-ayurveda-retreats-in-kerala\">Ayurveda Retreats in Kerala<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Part of this spiritual, natural way of living is Ayurveda medicine. This is a natural healing process that involves balancing your mind, lifestyle, diet, and energy. This type of healing is particularly popular in Kerala because of the abundance of medicinal herbs and plants used for Ayurvedic treatments. <\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105833\/india-Ayurveda-Retreats-567x810.jpg\" alt=\"india Ayurveda Retreats\"><\/noscript><img width=\"237\" height=\"338\" alt=\"india Ayurveda Retreats\" data-id=\"46703\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105833\/india-Ayurveda-Retreats.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?attachment_id=46703\" class=\"wp-image-46703 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 567px) 100vw, 567px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105833\/india-Ayurveda-Retreats-567x810.jpg 567w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105833\/india-Ayurveda-Retreats-300x429.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com