tains-1080x720.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-to-explore-the-kerala-coast\">To Explore the Kerala Coast<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Kerala is even blessed with a beautiful coastline! Red earthy cliffs topped with tilted palm tree forests blow in the breeze, above blue waters that lap the white sandy shores. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105859\/karela-india-beach.jpg\" alt=\"kerala india beach\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"338\" alt=\"kerala india beach\" class=\"wp-image-46686 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105859\/karela-india-beach.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105859\/karela-india-beach-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105859\/karela-india-beach-600x450.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105859\/karela-india-beach-800x600.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105859\/karela-india-beach-1080x810.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105859\/karela-india-beach-450x338.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105859\/karela-india-beach-1536x1151.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105859\/karela-india-beach-30x22.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105859\/karela-india-beach-163x122.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105859\/karela-india-beach-240x180.jpg 240w, https:\/\/st