&#x2019;s worth taking your chances at one of the national parks such as Periyar or Wayana. Even if you don&#x2019;t see a tiger, the experience of safari is hard to beat for animal lovers and adventurers.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105913\/kerala-india-elephant.jpg\" alt=\"kerala india elephant\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"kerala india elephant\" class=\"wp-image-46680 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105913\/kerala-india-elephant.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105913\/kerala-india-elephant-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105913\/kerala-india-elephant-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105913\/kerala-india-elephant-800x533.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105913\/kerala-india-elephant-1080x720.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105913\/kerala-india-elephant-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105913\/kerala-india-elephant-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105913\/kerala-india-elephant-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105913\/kerala-india-elephant-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105913\/kerala-india-elephant-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105913\/kerala-india-elephant-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/