d\">To Taste the Kerala Food!<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Keralan curries are famous the world over! They are spicy, use coconut, freshly caught seafood, and have a much fresher lighter taste than northern curries. Not only do they taste delicious, but they are beautiful too; colorfully served on a green banana leaf.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105840\/india-spices-577x810.jpg\" alt=\"india spices\"><\/noscript><img width=\"241\" height=\"338\" alt=\"india spices\" data-id=\"46698\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105840\/india-spices.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?attachment_id=46698\" class=\"wp-image-46698 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 577px) 100vw, 577px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105840\/india-spices-577x810.jpg 577w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105840\/india-spices-300x421.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105840\/india-spices-600x842.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105840\/india-spices-428x600.jpg 428w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105840\/india-spices-241x338.jpg 241w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105840\/india-spices-1094x1536.jpg 1094w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105840\/india-spices-21x30.jpg 21w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105840\/india-spices-116x163.jpg 116w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105840\/india-spices-128x180.jpg 128w, https: