ela-india-market-450x316.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105856\/karela-india-market-1536x1078.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105856\/karela-india-market-30x21.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105856\/karela-india-market-163x114.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105856\/karela-india-market-256x180.jpg 256w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105856\/karela-india-market-768x539.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105856\/karela-india-market-1024x719.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105856\/karela-india-market-1440x1011.jpg 1440w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105856\/karela-india-market-30x21.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105856\/karela-india-market.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-to-enjoy-beautiful-weather\">To Enjoy Beautiful Weather<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Kerala has warm temperatures all year round, as well as monsoon rains that make the countryside luscious and green. Different seasons are good for different things, depending on what you want. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.